1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,090
Each time you speak up, you strengthen yourself.
2
00:00:03,440 --> 00:00:06,129
Come forward with your constructive ideas.
3
00:00:06,720 --> 00:00:10,530
We all know how many college students prepare their assignments.
4
00:00:10,720 --> 00:00:16,929
With fine intentions, Joe College sets aside a whole evening for some concentrated study.
5
00:00:17,280 --> 00:00:21,570
Here is a general pattern of how, too often, the evening is spent.
6
00:00:22,879 --> 00:00:28,929
Joe's ready to begin studying at 7 p.m., but his dinner seems just a bit heavy,
7
00:00:28,960 --> 00:00:31,490
so he decides to get in a little TV.
8
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:36,610
A little turns out to be an hour's worth, since the program was pretty good.
9
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:44,450
At eight p.m., he sits down at his desk but gets right back up because he just remembered he promised to call his girl.
10
00:00:44,639 --> 00:00:46,610
This shoots another forty minutes.
11
00:00:46,639 --> 00:00:48,530
He hadn't talked to her all day.
12
00:00:48,720 --> 00:00:51,730
An incoming call takes another twenty minutes.
13
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:56,050
On his way back to his desk, Joe is drawn into a ping-pong game.
14
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:57,649
Another hour gone.
15
00:00:57,920 --> 00:01:01,649
The ping-pong makes him feel sweaty, so he takes a shower.
16
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:03,650
Next, he needs a snack.
17
00:01:03,919 --> 00:01:08,130
The combined effect of the ping-pong and the shower have made him hungry.
18
00:01:08,719 --> 00:01:12,770
And so the evening planned with good intentions drifts away.
19
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:18,770
Finally, at 1 a.m., he opens the book, but he's too sleepy to absorb the subject.
20
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:21,489
Finally, he surrenders completely.
21
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:25,969
Next morning, he tells the professor, I hope you give me a break.
22
00:01:26,080 --> 00:01:29,090
I studied till 2 a.m. for this exam.
23
00:01:30,319 --> 00:01:36,690
Joe College didn't get into action because he spent too much time getting ready to get into action.
24
00:01:36,879 --> 00:01:36,879
And Joe College isn't alone in being a victim of over-preparedness.
